Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,That's him! The guy we saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.40,GEM,,0,0,0,,So, you're the one who did this to the village, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.80,GEM,,0,0,0,,Were you trying to do the same thing to Resembool, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.70,GEM,,0,0,0,,What is your purpose for all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.20,GEM,,0,0,0,,What was that transmutation circle for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:29.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling we'd meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.20,GEM,,0,0,0,,Damn it, pal. You got a bad habit of being cryptic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.60,GEM,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.60,GEM,,0,0,0,,No circles. Impressive, young alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Interesting. You have the same eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,You should have realized you have no right to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Crowley!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:25.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,That's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,There could be no mistaking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:35.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Don't you recognize me? It's me! It's Arlen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Crowley?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:45.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,The Arlen I know is not a doddering old fool like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You're talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,How many years do you think it's been?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,How can you still look so young?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,Crowley!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,There he goes again. He just melted away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,You're safe now, Lieutenant Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,So how are you faring after all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Does it look like I'm all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor and tell the Colonel to double my salary, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.50,GEM,,0,0,0,,I mean, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:39.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,How come no one ever tells me how dangerous these missions are gonna be?
